        {
            "title": "劉香萍於亞視總台慶祝67歲生日 籌備開拍AI科幻片 唔排除與愛女貝安琪孫仔三代同堂演出",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"劉香萍於亞視總台慶祝67歲生日  籌備開拍AI科幻新片 唔排除與愛女貝安琪孫仔三代同堂演出\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/2916643b47bfbf5da0a79501b092ed50/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250402/_2025040222194078120.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">劉香萍於亞視總台慶祝67歲生日  籌備開拍AI科幻新片 唔排除與愛女貝安琪孫仔三代同堂演出</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>劉香萍今日（2日）迎來67歲生日，她於亞視總台慶生，女兒貝安琪、女婿Simon及8歲孫仔Sebastian均現身出席，更即場唱生日歌為劉香萍賀壽。\n\n</p><h2>希望孫仔聰明伶俐</h2>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"劉香萍今日迎來67歲生日。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/22315acd959320ec500d7b2fbc192f6f/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_7_56_36_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉香萍今日迎來67歲生日。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"女兒貝安琪、8歲孫仔Sebastian均有現身。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6e8c676916253056088e4c053bbc73da/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_7_56_33_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女兒貝安琪、8歲孫仔Sebastian均有現身。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"孫仔向劉香萍送「吻」祝賀。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bc2838355ae18fbded4fd5936e55e0f5/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_7_56_34_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        孫仔向劉香萍送「吻」祝賀。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"劉香萍生日願望希望孫仔聰明伶俐，家人身體健康。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/470917c745c2240a0ed6c2fc53a806e7/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_7_56_34_PM_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉香萍生日願望希望孫仔聰明伶俐，家人身體健康。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貝安琪與老公Simon。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/098a2e52268809720c43882c4889e352/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_7_56_35_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貝安琪與老公Simon。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"貝安琪一家三口好幸福！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c1873b6d1a657d2aec281a0cf718ae4c/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_7_56_35_PM_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        貝安琪一家三口好幸福！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"女兒貝安琪、女婿Simon及8歲孫仔即場唱生日歌為劉香萍賀壽。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4792512c66b15399dc7dba3faafece30/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_7_56_37_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        女兒貝安琪、女婿Simon及8歲孫仔即場唱生日歌為劉香萍賀壽。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"劉香萍與好友們。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6cdff080796c2bf8bbb90b16e9fe7397/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_7_56_37_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉香萍與好友們。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"劉香萍透露籌備開拍AI的科幻新片《100秒》，唔排除與愛女貝安琪孫仔三代同堂演出。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fa3c177b6b23ced876103148fa5a97d1/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_7_56_38_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉香萍透露籌備開拍AI的科幻新片《100秒》，唔排除與愛女貝安琪孫仔三代同堂演出。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曾效力麗的劉香萍說，重臨亞視感覺似回娘家的懷抱。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0c98cb474be38442c4274c2f5db3522a/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-02_at_7_56_38_PM_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曾效力麗的劉香萍說，重臨亞視感覺似回娘家的懷抱。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<p>劉香萍表示曾效力麗的，重臨亞視感覺似回娘家的懷抱，至於生日願望希望孫仔聰明伶俐，家人身體健康。在旁孫仔即爆金句：「要多啲錢！」相當搞笑。而劉香萍表示執導兼編劇電影《一棵心中的許願樹》，將會在大灣區1300間戲院上映，預計暑假檔期，又認為該片談及跨國文化，所以很適合中國年青人入場觀看，又指會籌備開拍關於AI的科幻新片《100秒》，一年前已寫好劇本。她說：「呢部新戲當然想囡囡貝安琪演出，孫仔都話有興趣，仲話自己好搞笑。」孫仔笑言對演戲有興趣，尤其喜歡喜劇，又自認好搞笑，但爸爸比他更搞笑。問到他是否收很高片酬，他即點頭笑言：「係。」劉香萍則謂不排除自己會演個小角色，屆時可以三代同堂演出。談到可會讓兒子參與幕前演出，貝安琪笑指兒子不怕醜，只要對演戲有熱誠不妨可嘗試。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
