            "title": "警方荃灣掃黃拘10內地女 介乎36至56歲",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警方荃灣掃黃拘10內地女 介乎36至56歲。警方圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f4362c389099a6d7a4e6cb94fb1dc956/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250402/_2025040222352341913.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警方荃灣掃黃拘10內地女 介乎36至56歲。警方圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>荃灣警區特別職務隊聯同入境事務處，根據線報及經深入調查後，今日（四月二日）展開代號「嶺馬」的掃黃行動。行動中，人員在川龍街，河背街及兆和街一帶拘捕10名內地女子，年齡介乎36至56歲，涉嫌「違反逗留條件」。所有被捕女子正被扣留調查，稍後將交由相關部門跟進。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4174004/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"所有被捕女子正被扣留調查。警方圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/03960ebf183b4ae9b86055a46b8c8c08/2025-04/MIU_Landmaster_1_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        所有被捕女子正被扣留調查。警方圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
