            "title": "上海女清明燒冥鏹  焚毀鄰居保時捷賠¥15萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"上海張女士近日燒冥鏹引燃鄰居保時捷。看看新聞\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/230bcf7cf6e07b24e89d07353bf48af2/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250402/_2025040221464236628.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">上海張女士近日燒冥鏹引燃鄰居保時捷。看看新聞</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>清明臨近，民眾焚香、燒衣，祭祀先人的活動日多。上海有女民眾，近日因為燒冥鏹時，灰燼未完全熄滅便倒入垃圾桶，導致起火把旁邊的保時捷汽車燒毀，需要向鄰居賠償巨款。\n\n</p>\n<p>據上觀新聞報道，3月28日，上海楊浦區河間路一個屋苑，居民張女士燒衣祭祖後，隨手將未熄滅的紙錢灰燼倒入路邊的垃圾桶。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"上海張女士近日燒冥鏹引燃鄰居保時捷。看看新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ec355649da76b972664fdacc926f5ab5/2025-04/002.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        上海張女士近日燒冥鏹引燃鄰居保時捷。看看新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"上海張女士近日燒冥鏹引燃鄰居保時捷。看看新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a6d0818ed57e600ef7644b59e4822f6c/2025-04/4554.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        上海張女士近日燒冥鏹引燃鄰居保時捷。看看新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"上海張女士近日燒冥鏹引燃鄰居保時捷。看看新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/34702edd2704626a0b391a8706b15c06/2025-04/456564.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        上海張女士近日燒冥鏹引燃鄰居保時捷。看看新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"上海張女士近日燒冥鏹引燃鄰居保時捷。看看新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3343d313c7d71897b934ec3ea003f355/2025-04/54645656.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        上海張女士近日燒冥鏹引燃鄰居保時捷。看看新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"上海張女士近日燒冥鏹引燃鄰居保時捷。看看新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c35359e915defc61be2caf7a6a9e4846/2025-04/455465263.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        上海張女士近日燒冥鏹引燃鄰居保時捷。看看新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/china-topics/3441185/%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E6%B1%BD%E8%BB%8A%E6%89%93%E9%80%9A%E9%99%B0%E9%99%BD%E5%85%A9%E7%95%8C-%E6%B8%85%E6%98%8E%E7%AF%80%E7%B4%99%E7%B4%AESU7%E7%86%B1%E8%B3%A3\">小米汽車打通陰陽兩界 清明節紙紮SU7熱賣</a>\n</p>\n<p>幾分鐘後，餘燼死灰復燃，引燃垃圾桶內的可燃物，迅速變成熊熊大火。\n\n</p>\n<p>從現場閉路電視可見，大火將停泊在垃圾桶旁的一輛保時捷跑車引燃燒毀。\n\n</p>\n<p>事件雖未造成人命傷亡，但張女士需要承擔約15萬元人民幣的維修費。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
